ault and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSSuggestionChip","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip","role":"symbol","title":"OUDSSuggestionChip"},"ic_folder_categories.png":{"type":"image","alt":null,"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/ic_folder_categories.png"}]}}}